    "zh": "2022 年规则将 F1 轮毂由 13 英寸一举提升至 18 英寸，并强制安装标准轮辋罩，彻底重塑了车轮的机械结构与空气动力学角色。",
    "en": "The 2022 rules jumped F1 rims from 13 to 18 inches and mandated standard covers, reshaping the wheel's mechanical structure and aerodynamic role."
  },
